oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Benny Martin Show with Bun Wilson at the Country Music Jamboree
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Martin, Benny
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (black and red on white) Hatch poster announcing Bun Wilson's Country Music Jamboree with the Benny Martin Show featuring Eddy Dunlap, Charlie Thurman and the Dam busters, and others on June 20-22. Poster features metal photoplates of Benny Martin and Eddy Dunlap.
